figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">比特幣 (BitfinexUSD)升0.09%，在6.5萬美元上方徘徊。Coinglass數據顯示，最近24小時，加密貨幣市場超8萬人爆倉，爆倉金額達2.75億美元。</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"美股開市前，英特爾績後升5%！布油破百後跳水，黃金反彈升至4050美元\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/lo/mysterio/api/fa86461e1ef8401f67e6f4d30b36ed32dd5d19795b4794372bfe5980fd654d7c/lightyear_networkapi/resizefill_w960;quality_80;format_webp/https:%2F%2Fcontent-media.investing.com%2Fhk%2Fcontent%2Fb4e82ba6c25fd70b24c97853f4c54fb2.png\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">美股開市前，英特爾績後升5%！布油破百後跳水，黃金反彈升至4050美元</figcaption></div></figure><blockquote class=\"border-pebble mx-5 my-7.5 border-l-2 pl-5 italic\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-dolphin\"><strong>七月限時開搶！InvestingPro 4折到手，AI選股名單即刻用，跑贏標普500近3倍，全年冇更平，錯過就走寶！</strong><a data-yga='{\"yInteractivityType\":\"0\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yLinkText\":\"即刻點擊訂閱\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:即刻點擊訂閱;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;\" href=\"https://hk.investing.com/pro/pricing?utm_medium=feed&amp;utm_source=yahoo&amp;utm_campaign=yahoo-hk\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><strong><em>即刻點擊訂閱</em></strong></a><strong>！</strong></p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"美股開市前，英特爾績後升5%！布油破百後跳水，黃金反彈升至4050美元\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/lo/mysterio/api/e390ed9d558eeef2c68356ad579e49e9b6e23250c1b9b8716013b95bb3f2be1d/lightyear_networkapi/resizefill_w960;quality_80;format_webp/https:%2F%2Fcontent-media.investing.com%2Fhk%2Fcontent%2F1b5455b84f36290884a6d2b5da899224.png\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width: