            "title": "Arcadis股價飆升至九個月高位，Jefferies上調評級看好盈利復甦",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\" data-component=\"blocks\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"Arcadis股價飆升至九個月高位，Jefferies上調評級看好盈利復甦\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"540\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/lo/mysterio/api/5d3bdcfca5dbc769ae2511aa4368cc86ff7aed8619553f1bb6a1654b7c568a32/lightyear_networkapi/resizefill_w960;quality_80;format_webp/https:%2F%2Fcontent-media.investing.com%2Fnews%2FBullish_M_1440047649.jpg\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">Arcadis股價飆升至九個月高位，Jefferies上調評級看好盈利復甦</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 荷蘭工程諮詢公司<a data-yga='{\"yInteractivityType\":0,\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\"}' data-ylk=\"elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;\" href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/tag/Arcadis\" rel=\"\">Arcadis</a>（AS:ARDS）股價週五大漲逾5%，此前<a data-yga='{\"yInteractivityType\":0,\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\"}' data-ylk=\"elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;\" href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/tag/Jefferies\" rel=\"\">Jefferies</a>將其評級上調至「買入」，理由是隨著利潤率回升，盈利質量持續改善，加之股價經歷長期跑輸大市後估值吸引力明顯提升。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Arcadis股價上漲5%至41.38歐元，創下自去年10月底以來的最高水平，表現遠優於同期上漲0.3%的AEX指數。Jefferies同時將目標價由39.50歐元上調至48歐元，較前一個交易日收盤價高出約22%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-443a27e5-5123-30b1-8314-5690926cb2e5-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Jefferies指出，Arcadis定於7月30日公布的第二季業績將是下一個重要催化劑，預計持續改善的盈利勢頭將進一步推動估值重估。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Jefferies表示，隨著公司的重組計劃及削減成本舉措開始轉化為實際運營表現的提升，目前的風險回報比已更為有利。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">該行預計，隨著裁員措施、間接費用節省以及更嚴格的項目篩選機制在未來數個季度逐步發揮效益，公司利潤率將持續回升。更強勁的執行力亦有望抵銷房地產及投資業務持續疲弱所帶來的拖累。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Arcadis在水利基礎設施、能源轉型、環境服務及數字工程等領域具備長期需求優勢，項目管線持續改善，有望支撐公司重返有機增長軌道。儘管具備上述利好因素，Jefferies認為Arcadis股價相對歐洲同業工程公司仍存在不合理的折讓，意味著估值仍有進一步重估的空間。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">投資者亦將密切關注公司在重組進度、各主要終端市場需求狀況，以及公司在近期股東回報計劃後有關資本配置方向的最新表態。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/arcadis%E8%82%A1%E5%83%B9%E9%A3%86%E5%8D%87%E8%87%B3%E4%B9%9D%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E9%AB%98%E4%BD%8D-jefferies%E4%B8%8A%E8%AA%BF%E8%A9%95%E7%B4%9A%E7%9C%8B%E5%A5%BD%E7%9B%88%E5%88%A9%E5%BE%A9%E7%94%A6-100406757.html",
